"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"cc08424e-6ed2-4747-92b0-c242244c8250\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T00:10:58.853554905Z\"\"}\",出现次数:26\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"ca1ec12f-0fd2-4563-b53d-4498853284d0\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"64ea5975-02ba-478a-b21b-803071b208fa\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T00:17:43.535962403Z\"\"}\",出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"326eb266-a9c1-4b37-bd32-d92cb64b211c\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"a4f0a37a-bd06-481b-8382-a45c93382a50\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T00:10:25.943606563Z\"\"}\",出现次数:13\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-1", "frontend-2"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-19T00:10:09Z to 2025-06-19T00:26:09Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 00:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-19 00:26:09+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"dial tcp\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\", \"rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"端口连接被拒绝 - 多个frontend服务实例报告连接paymentservice时出现connection refused错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析发现：\n\n**关键发现**：\n- 所有错误日志都来自 `frontend` 服务的三个不同实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n- 错误模式一致：在调用 `/cart/checkout` 接口时，frontend服务尝试连接 `paymentservice` 时遇到连接拒绝\n- 目标地址：`10.233.55.4:50051`（推测为paymentservice的IP和端口）\n\n**故障模式识别**：\n- 这是一个典型的 **Port Misconfiguration** 故障\n- 根据特殊故障模式识别规则，`component` 应设置为被调方服务（paymentservice）\n- `detected_log_keys` 中包含了 `connection refused` 和 `port` 相关的关键词\n\n**影响范围**：\n- 故障影响了所有frontend实例，导致用户无法完成订单支付流程\n- 错误发生频率较高（出现次数从2次到32次不等），表明这是一个持续性的连接问题\n\n当前处于初始扫描阶段，已识别出主要的异常调用链和故障模式。下一步可以进行更深入的根因分析。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态码显示大量连接拒绝错误：'dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused'，出现81次，是根因错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"作为paymentservice的直接调用方，传播错误到frontend，出现34次错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice->redis调用延迟从1.77ms剧增到11.74ms，延迟倍数6.6倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend->shipping调用延迟从1.8-1.9ms增加到3.5-4.0ms，延迟倍数约2倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend->currency调用延迟从2.3ms增加到4.7ms，延迟倍数2倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作延迟从9-11ms增加到11-13ms，部分ListProducts操作延迟增加3倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n**根因分析**：paymentservice服务完全不可用（连接被拒绝），这是导致整个系统故障的根因。错误从paymentservice传播到checkoutservice，再传播到frontend。\n\n**延迟问题**：\n- redis服务出现显著延迟（6.6倍）\n- shipping和currency服务出现中等延迟（约2倍）\n- productcatalogservice部分操作有轻微延迟\n\n**错误传播路径**：paymentservice → checkoutservice → frontend，导致前端返回500错误。", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio and error_ratio increased significantly during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.27; error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.27\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio and error_ratio increased significantly during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.28; error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.28\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio and error_ratio increased significantly during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.31; error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.31\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes changed from 1.0 to 2.0, indicating a possible pod restart or crash.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: normal_median=1.0, fault_median=1.0, normal_p99=1.0, fault_p99=2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased significantly, indicating potential memory pressure.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: normal_median=5081673728.0, fault_median=4168708096.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: normal_median=7966.0, fault_median=9178.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly during the fault period.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: normal_median=3376.0, fault_median=3362.0, normal_p99=9226.04, fault_p99=38106.95\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}
